<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> rapuramu <unclear>nīśānaṁbu</unclear>na guḍi nilpinadi <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> reya maṟevuṇani nallataṇḍayna Ayyaparāju tammuṇḍu bejeya 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇḍu guṇakenallaṇḍu vancina paṇḍaraṁgavūra paṇḍaraṁgu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> rutaṁbu daṇḍanāthu nacalapuramu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ccena calituṇḍu valla <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> cōḍani jēkoni kāci bhūlōkaṁ beṟuṁga kiranapuramu dahiñcina <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>venājilō <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> ṇḍanu <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> vaccina <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>baiki rāhavu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ḍicina vallabhu kolvuna nella neṟuṁga kannarabhū<unclear>pā</unclear> 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> nnalarāju<unclear>vi</unclear>bhutōḍana daṟi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ya <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> naḍavi socce <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> na 
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> mahīmaṇḍalaprakāśitakīrtti śrīmatpaṇḍaraṁgu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> pudurgga <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> stiti dharmmuvurammuna svastyanēkaguṇagaṇālaṁkritu vi <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>jayarājya saṁvatsaraṁbu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> gu nēṇṭi Uttarāyanasaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>Note.—The greater portion of this inscription seems to be in Telugu verse but, as it is mostly illegible, the verses cannot be reconstructed.</p>

<p>This inscription is published in <hi rend="italic">Nellore Inscriptions,</hi> pp. 966 f. but the reading there is incorrect in places.</p>

